      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Some gnomes exult in their own effort and seem inured to pain. These gnomes gain a +2 species bonus to saves against pain effects. Once per day when they roll a natural 20 on an attack roll, skill check, or saving throw, they gain a rush of adrenaline that grants them a +1 morale bonus to attack rolls, saving throws, and skill checks for 2 rounds.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces eternal hope.</strong></p>\n<p><em>Use @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.htNsUPes8JFuF51W]{Ecstatic Joy (+1 Morale)} for tracking daily usage.</em></p>"
